  "decision_conditions": [
    "Condition : 1 - The proposed rear extension, with a maximum depth of 4.15m would be contrary to the provisions of Section 1.0 of the Residential Extension Guidelines, causing harm to neighbouring amenities by reason of loss of outlook and increased sense of enclosure, contrary to policies CC1, CC2 and SC7 of the Local Plan.\r\nFurthermore, the erection of such a deep extension would set a negative precedent in the area which due to its location on a prominent corner would cause harm to the character and appearance of the host building and the general streetscene, contrary to policies CC1 and CC2 of the Local Plan."
